data.description: Nestled in the vibrant heart of Freeport Village, this classic California bungalow provides desirable proximity to both downtown and the Sacramento River. This enviable location seamlessly combines convenience, style, and natural beauty. Charming front porch offers plenty of space for seating and an ideal spot for container gardening. Inside you'll find laminate flooring and crown molding plus a host of recent done-for-you updates. Roomy kitchen features Shaker-style cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances plus an adjoining dining area. Enjoy the convenience of an oversized single-bay attached garage with laundry room. Privacy-fenced outdoor space features hardscape and greenspace, offering plenty of options for outdoor seating, grilling, dining and entertaining under an inviting shade tree. Close proximity to the Sacramento River offers recreational river access, plus nearby William Land Park as well as shopping, dining and easy access to major thoroughfares Hwy 5 and Hwy 99.
